Package: sparseHessianFD
Type: Package
Title: Numerical Estimation of Sparse Hessians
Version: 0.3.0
Date: 2015-05-04
Authors@R: person(family="Braun", given="Michael", role=c("aut","cre","cph"), email="braunm@smu.edu")
URL: coxprofs.cox.smu.edu/braunm
Description: Estimates Hessian of a scalar-valued function, and returns it in a sparse Matrix format. The sparsity pattern must be known in advance.  The algorithm is especially efficient for hierarchical models with a large number of heterogeneous units.
License: MPL (== 2.0)
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    Matrix (>= 1.2.0),
    methods
Suggests:
    testthat,
    numDeriv,
    knitr
Roxygen: list(wrap=TRUE)
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen (>= 0.3.2.3)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
SystemRequirements: C++11
